{"tid":477492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[德望風波?]影女生裙底判囚　被告指港鐵站人多難發現","createTime":"2017-11-23T06:01:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-23T17:05:28.000Z","uid":92983,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a6a81704aa29daaec2b9f44227b2b2109bb39607","tid":477492,"uid":92983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T06:01:03.000Z","msg":"男貨倉助理自今年9月起，多次在港鐵站內偷拍女士裙底，當中更包括有穿校服的女生，最終有警員日前在港鐵彩虹站內巡邏時，見他形迹可疑，於是上前截查，揭發他先後用兩部手機拍攝共25張裙底照和4段裙底片。他今(23日)在九龍城法院承認3項作出有違公德的行為罪，<span style=\"color: red;\">判囚6星期</span>。<br />\n<br />\n控方透露，39歲被告戚志邦有一項同類案底，另於2013年有一項在公眾地方行為不檢的案底。辯方求情指他未婚，<span style=\"color: red;\">並沒有將涉案片段和相片上載</span>，已感後悔。<br />\n<br />\n案情透露，警員於11月21日在彩虹站進行便衣巡邏，見被告可疑，於是截停他，揭發他用智能手錶遙控手提膠袋內的手機偷拍，警誡下他承認用手機拍攝校服女生的裙底照，又指因港鐵站人多，不易被發現，故喜歡到港鐵站犯案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171123/bkn-20171123123818769-1123_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171123%2Fbkn-20171123123818769-1123_00822_001.html&d=7Z0xoBeOu75rHjV%2FsWjGitr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=25ff1e5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171123/bkn-20171123123818769-1123_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a29c169330a2450a693c7018efc31be078bf3f82","tid":477492,"uid":92983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T06:07:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e34c7250a798b2b8e0f321467ce43a463c26f3fd","tid":477492,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T06:08:20.000Z","msg":"咁快審得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e7719580791fceea3e16d10405ef03caa1f157","tid":477492,"uid":20867,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T06:13:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁快審得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n簽學承認<br />\n街拍女生<br />\n無須審判<br />\n即時槍決"},{"pid":"9